Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.82,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Anything on the fugitive demons?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:15.46,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I apologize, but there have been\Nno developments whatsoever.}Rất xin lỗi nhưng không có bất cứ tin gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:18.45,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I see. But it's already been two years...}Vậy à, cũng 2 năm rồi nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:21.19,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't be surprised to \Nsee some major movement soon.}Có lẽ chúng cũng sắp hành động.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:23.33,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I'm curious about something.}Tôi có điều cần hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:26.90,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{What kind of demon does one turn \Ninto if not fused with a human?}Ác quỷ sẽ thành gì nếu không hợp\N nhất với con người?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:33.20,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{They'd be a giant creature \Nwith no rigidly defined form}Trở thành một sinh vật khổng lồ\N không có hình dạng xác định
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.34,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{whose body is made out of these tentacles.}và cơ thể có những xúc tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:38.82,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Cory-kun seems to have a lot \Nof eyes. What about that?}Cory có nhiều mắt. Như thế là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.47,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{We all have a lot of eyes,}Chúng tôi đều có nhiều mắt,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.86,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{but most of them look inward after fusing,}nhưng hầu hết chúng đều\N chui vào trong sau khi hợp nhất,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.12,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{so they're hard to confirm.}nên rất khó để thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:47.73,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Pardon me...}Xin chờ chút...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:51.42,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I've actually got a visible one in my mouth.}Tôi cũng có một con trong miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.49,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Not that it serves any purpose—}Nó cũng chả có tác dụng--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.16,Main,Barcde,0,0,0,,{Ysley-dono, do you have a moment?}Cậu có rảnh không Ysley?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.54,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's got a thin, transparent eyelid, \Nlike a frog's...}Có mí mắt, tròng mắt... như mắt ếch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.29,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Could you open a bit wider...?}Mở to ra chút nào...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.52,Main,Barcode,0,0,0,,{Am I interrupting something?}Xin thứ lỗi vì đã làm phiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:10.86,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{N-No! That's... It's not what \Nyou're thinking, Barcode.}K-Không phải! Không phải như ông nghĩ đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:13.05,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Sorry. My curiosity got the better of me.}Xin lỗi, tôi hơi tập trung quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:13.95,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{So?}Thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:16.15,Main,Barcode,0,0,0,,{Well, it turns out...}Chuyện là...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:23.68,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{So you couldn't control your child\N and have come to us for help?}Không thể kiểm soát đứa con nên đến đây nhờ trợ giúp?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:28.07,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I see. The exact kind of major \Nmovement he was anticipating...}Ra là vậy. Hóa ra đây là hành động mà ngài ấy nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:32.69,Main,Meliano,0,0,0,,{Piscalat! You've got to help him!}Piscalat! Xin hãy cứu thằng bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.96,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{How old is he at this point?}Nó sinh được bao lâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.96,Main,Buzz,0,0,0,,{Around two months.}Khoảng 2 tháng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:43.08,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{You'll have to give up, then. Demons can't \Nfuse after hitting the two-week mark.}Bỏ cuộc đi. Quỷ không thể hợp nhất sau 2 tuần.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:48.11,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Demons who fail to fuse during that\N two-week period are disposed of, as well.}Những con quỷ không hợp nhất\N trong 2 tuần đều bị loại bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.31,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Did you not know that?}Không biết điều đó sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.34,Main,Meliano,0,0,0,,{Oh, no...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:55.84,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{That aside, Buzz, do you know anything \Nabout the other demons who escaped?}Quan trọng hơn Buzz, cậu có biết\N vị trí những kẻ trốn thoát không?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.51,Main,Buzz,0,0,0,,{It's like I already told you.}Tôi đã nói rồi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.49,Main,Buzz,0,0,0,,{We didn't discuss our plans.\NWe just fled in different directions...}chúng tôi không liên quan đến nhau.\N Mỗi người chạy một hướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.35,Italics,Buzz,0,0,0,,{Wait, something's weird here.}Khoan, có gì đó không ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.85,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{And you don't know anything either, Meliano?}Và cô cũng không biết gì, Meliano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:10.10,Main,Meliano,0,0,0,,{I don't! I've been with Buzz all this time!}Không! Tôi ở bên Buzz suốt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:14.11,Italics,Buzz,0,0,0,,{Piscalat's already suspicious \Nof everything I'm saying...}Piscalat đã nghi ngờ những gì mình nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:17.32,Italics,Buzz,0,0,0,,{What do I do? Grab Meliano and run?}Sao giờ? Mang Meliano và chạy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.66,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Looks like we're done with you, in that case.}Vậy thì không cần đến các ngươi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.00,Main,Buzz,0,0,0,,M-Meliano...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.50,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I definitely prefer seafood.}Quả nhiên cá vẫn ngon hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.25,Main,Buzz,0,0,0,,{You bastard!}Thằng khốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.35,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{You've gotten a lot more powerful.}Hôm nay khỏe nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.28,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{You might even be more stronger \Nthan Nickel was, Cory.}Cậu còn mạnh hơn Nikel nhỉ, Cory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.47,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Well, who can say for sure?}Chả biết nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.43,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{It might've been fun to find out\Nif Nickel were still alive.}Nếu Nikel còn sống thì mới so được.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:52.68,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{So they hid on a deserted island, \Ncompletely isolating themselves...}Chúng trốn trên đảo hoang và cô lập hoàn toàn à.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.52,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I see. A bad choice, though.}Không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.89,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Fleeing in a way that you sacrifice\Nall intel regarding the enemy,}Chạy trốn và từ bỏ tim kiếm thông tin kẻ thù,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.61,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{in exchange for a greater \Nsense of security...}đổi lại được an toàn tuyệt đối...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.21,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's the same as when \Npeople spend their lives}Cũng như một kẻ dành cả cuộc đời
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.97,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{doing nothing for fear of failure.}chẳng làm gì ngoài sợ hãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.57,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{The ultimate result...}Kết quả tất yếu...
