Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.26,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Take that... And that! And that! And that!}Nhận lấy! Nhận lấy! Nhận lấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.53,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{You okay, Gill-san?}Ổn chứ Gill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.62,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'm fine... I can keep going...}Tôi ổn... vẫn tiếp tục được...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:17.75,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{I really don't think so.\NYour legs are pointing the wrong way.}Thật à... Thân cô quay ngược lại luôn kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.96,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Damn, are you two down for the count already?} Hết dậy nổi rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:25.37,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{This sucks. Granny's still dead on her feet, \Nand Prontea doesn't show up anymore...}Chán thật. Bà già chết tiệt kia vẫn như vậy, \NProntea thì chẳng xuất hiện mấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:28.01,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{You seem kinda bored, Hayato.}Có vẻ đang chán nhỉ, anh Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.14,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Why not fight me?}Chiến một trận không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:36.20,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Who're you again?}Thằng nào đấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.14,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,1)\an9\fnArial\b1\c&HC39763&\3c&H5D115E&\bord3\shad0\pos(628,106.667)}{Urgh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.85,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{He looks pretty different, \Nbut I think that's Cory-kun.}Trông hơi khác nhưng tớ nghĩ là Cory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.39,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Oh, Cory...}À Cory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.53,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Come on! Get a grip.}Thôi nào! Nghiêm túc đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.97,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Okay, guess we're doing this.}À ừm. Vậy thì đánh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.78,Italics,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Cory who, though?}Cory? Thằng nào vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:55.37,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Ysley taught me the best way to use my power!}Anh Ysley đã chỉ tôi cách sử dụng sức mạnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.13,Italics,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Oh, the kid with the morphing face.}À, thằng nhóc với khuôn mặt dị hợm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.89,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Now, I'm ready whenever you are!}Nào, thích lên lúc nào cũng được!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.22,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Nasty!}Thật khó chịu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.66,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{You two! Fight somewhere with more room!}Hai người tìm chỗ nào rộng mà đánh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.71,Italics,Hayato,0,0,0,,{He's strong! What the hell?}Mạnh thật! Nó là cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.34,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{You wanna take this somewhere else\N since Paula-chan's mad?}Chúng ta đổi chỗ khác đi nhỉ? Paula tức rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.70,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You gotta tell me one thing first.}Trước đó thì ta cần hỏi một câu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.75,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What training did you do\Nto get that much stronger so fast?}Ngươi huấn luyện kiểu gì mà\N mạnh lên nhanh quá vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:07:01.10,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{Training? I didn't do any. \NI just matured from a kid to an adult.}Huấn luyện? Em có làm gì đâu? Chỉ là trưởng thành thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:07.78,Main,Cory,0,0,0,,{A lion is a whole lot stronger after \Nit grows up, right? Same kinda thing.}Sư tử sẽ mạnh hơn khi \Ntrưởng thành, phải không? Em cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.28,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It's a bit unfair, isn't it?}Có hơi bất công nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.62,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Being guaranteed extra strength \Njust by getting older...}Tăng thêm sức mạnh chỉ bằng cách trưởng thành...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.06,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{I would think that the Idaten's \Nlimitless capacity for growth}Tôi nghĩ Idaten có khả năng phát triển vô hạn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.61,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{via training isn't much fairer.}thông qua luyện tập mới bất công chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.34,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Do you think Hayato can beat Cory?}Ngài nghĩ Hayato có đánh bại Cory không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.90,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Probably not, right?}Chắc là không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:30.38,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{That said, I could definitely win if I had\N the kind of strength Hayato does.}Nếu tôi có sức mạnh như\N Hayato thì nhất định sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.91,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{See, that fleshy armor of \Nhis has a sense of taste.}Cái lớp giáp nhớp nháp đó có cảm giác,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.23,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{So, hypothetically, \NI could spray him head to toe}nên theo giả thuyết tôi sẽ sử dụng hơi cay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.64,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{with extremely painful hot sauce...}và xịt vào để gây đau đớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.27,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{He'd be unable to focus on fighting.}Cậu ta sẽ không thể tập trung chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.85,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Alternately, I could do what \NI did when we fought.}Hoặc làm giống lần chiến đấu với cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.90,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{P-Please don't remind me!}Đ-Đừng làm tôi nhớ lại chuyện đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:52.00,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{But Hayato fights won strength alone,\N no strategy or tricks involved.}Nhưng Hayato chỉ chiến đấu\N đơn thuần mà không có chiến thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.13,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{But just like how a trained martial artist}Giống như những võ sĩ được huấn luyện,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.66,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{who's mastered all kinds\Nof techniques and tactics}thông thạo tất cả kĩ năng,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.01,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{pales in comparison to some wild bear...}nhưng đối thủ lại là gấu hoang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.22,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{There's a kind of extreme combat power \Nthat only an idiot is capable of mastering.}Chỉ đơn thuần là một tên ngốc với sức chiến đấu cực cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.52,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{That's what I want Hayato to achieve.}Đó là những gì tôi muốn Hayato hướng đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.07,Main,Baby,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.06,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Okay, here you go.}Đây đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.47,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Now say, "Ah!"}Aaa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.08,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{How are they doing, Merku?}Chúng sao rồi Merku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.02,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{There are no signs of fusion side effects,}Không có dấu hiệu của phản ứng phụ,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.66,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{and they're growing without trouble so far.}và chúng đang lớn lên bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:26.73,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Those are your future husbands, \Nso make sure you show them lots of love.}Chúng là chồng tương lai của cô đấy,\N nhớ phải yêu thương nhiều vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:30.03,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{I still just can't get behind that...}Tôi vẫn chưa quen với nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.77,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Say, Miku, are we seriously going \Nto do it with these kids?}Nè Miku, chúng ta nghiêm túc làm nó với chúng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.72,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Throw the TV on, would you, Merku?}Mở TV lên đi Merku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:36.78,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{The TV?}Tv?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:43.74,Italics,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}{As you can see, we've got a \Nclear shot of the monster!}Nhưng đã thấy, chúng tôi \Nđang quay cận cảnh con quái vật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:50.03,Italics,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}{It's pulling apart this passenger liner\N like it's shelling a crab!}Nó đang kéo chiếc tàu ra như một con cua xé mồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.50,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{That's...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.63,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Probably either Buzz or Raki. \NOne of their kids, anyway.}Có vẻ là của Buzz hoặc Raki. Con của một trong hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.54,Italics,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}{The ship has been split and two \Nand is now falling into the sea.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.26,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{And this is exactly what I was waiting for.}Và đây là điều kiện tôi đang chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:56.48,Italics,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}{That's quite a splash from the impact...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:59.01,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{With demons running amok out in the open, \Nthe Idaten are bound to focus on them.}Với con ác quỷ đó, đám Idaten sẽ tập trung vào nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.99,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{This will give us a chance to \Nrendezvous with the Demon Lord,}Nó sẽ cho chúng ta cơ hội tái hợp Quỷ vương,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:04.89,Italics,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}{There were an estimated five thousand \Npassengers on the ship— Agh!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:04.27,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{and start cooking up some plans!}và bắt đầu kế hoạch mới!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.27,Main,Deliveryman,0,0,0,,{Got a package for you.}Chuyển phát đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.27,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Hey, thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.03,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{A weird robot, a tiny camera, \Nand a digital camera...}Một con robot kì lạ, máy quay nhỏ\N và máy chụp ảnh KTS...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.28,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{What's the point of this stuff?}Mấy thứ này để làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.28,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{First, I take a picture of the robot.}Đầu tiên chụp ảnh robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.78,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Then I update the blog...}Sau đó đăng lên blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.53,Main - Top,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\fscy150\fnArial\fs18\b1\bord4\shad4\c&H252125&\3c&HEAEEEB&\4c&HEAEEEB&\pos(336,294.667)}{Impulse Purchase~\N\N }{\fs12\b0}{Something about his weird robot really struck me,\N so I ended up buying it~ ^^;\N I'm totally in love with how weird it looks, moving around\N so smoothly while it talks through it's radio (*^_^*)\N Maybe I'm weird too?\N Also splurged on a camera (boom)\N All these unplanned purchases (sob)\N I'm totally feeling batchyrogeh about it~ \N(Don't ask what that means*)\N I wonder if this is a good enough first picture? (omg omg)\N I'd love to post it moving around and talking\N but I don't know how to take video yet (^.^;\N Somebody *teach me* (begging for help lol)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.98,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{All done!}Xong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{What?}Xong cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.26,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{It's got speakers that \Ncan pick up radio waves,}Nó có bộ thu phát sóng radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.81,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{and it's pretty nimble, too...}và cũng khá nhanh nhẹn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:30.22,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Once the camera is installed, the Demon Lord \Ncan use it as a temporary body.}Camera cũng đã được gắn vào, Quỷ vương\N có thể dùng nó như cơ thể tạm thời.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.87,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{You couldn't do any better than this?}Cô không làm con nào đẹp hơn được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.09,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{That would've been expensive...}Mắc lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.62,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{So, how are you going \Nto tell him that blog is ours?}Nhưng sao ngài ấy biết được blog của chúng ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:40.05,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{The internet will do the job \Nfor me in due time.}Internet sẽ làm việc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:44.43,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{I anticipated everything up until \Nthis point when we went on the run.}Tôi đã đoán trước mọi chuyện cho đến lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.94,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Which is why the letter I gave His Lordship\N included a way to get in touch.}Đó là lý do tôi để lại bức thư\N cho ngài ấy cùng cách liên lạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.27,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Wait, really? Then you can just \Ncall him and let him know.}Tưởng gì. Vậy chỉ cần gọi cho ngài ấy là xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.66,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Not happening.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:57.69,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{I'm pretty sure the enemy \Nis connected to all telecom in Zoble,}Kẻ địch đã kết nối toàn bộ điện thoại ở Zoble,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.57,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{and there's no way to tell what phone number \Nhe might be using, wherever he is.}và không có cách nào biết được số ngài ấy sử dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.77,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Then what did you tell him?}Vậy cô để lại lời nhắn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.17,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{A nonsense phrase.}Một cụm từ vô nghĩa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.33,Main,zoomed in sign,0,0,0,,{\fscy150\fnArial\fs18\b1\bord4\shad4\c&H252125&\3c&HEAEEEB&\4c&HEAEEEB&\pos(322.909,125.94)}{feeling batchyrogeh about it~ (Don't ask what that means*)}Cảm thấy Batchyrogeh (Đừng hỏi nghĩa từ này)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.90,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{See this part of the blog post?}Thấy chỗ này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.98,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{What }{\i1}{does}{\i0}{ that mean?}Nó nghĩa là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.11,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Nothing at all. I made it up.}Không có nghĩa gì cả. Tôi chế ra thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.99,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{But that's what makes it special.}Nhưng chính vì thế mà nó lại có nghĩa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:20.57,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Because, at present, \Nthere are no hits for that word.}Vì hiện tại, không có lượt tìm kiếm nào cho từ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:21.95,Main,Button sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs16\bord0\shad0\fad(1,380)\pos(322.909,169.637)}{Search}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.12,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{So the first result for it now,}Thế nên kết quả đầu tiên,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.31,Main,Search field sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\b1\fnArial\fs18\pos(109.818,57.454)\c&H1F211F&\3c&HDDE0DE&\4c&HDDE0DE&}{feeling batchyrogeh}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.31,Main,Results sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\fs18\c&H1F211F&\3c&HDDE0DE&\4c&HDDE0DE&\pos(122.182,203.636)}{Your search "feeling batchyrogeh" yielded }{\b1}{0 results.}{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:29.26,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{no matter how stupid might seem, \Nmeans it's me!}là một trang blog vớ vẩn, cũng chính là chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:36.85,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{And as blatant a method as this is,\Nthere's no way to catch on to it.}Và một cách liên lạc như vậy chắc chắn sẽ không bị để ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:41.53,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Wait, Miku, once he knows that blog is yours,}Khoan đã Miku, sau khi ngài ấy biết về blog đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.83,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{are you just going to post the address here?}chẳng phải cô đã điền địa chỉ nơi này sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.18,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Wouldn't that be dangerous?}Liệu có nguy hiểm không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:50.23,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about, Merku? \NDon't you remember how I found this place?}Cô nói gì vậy Merku?\N Cô quên cách tôi tìm ra nơi này rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.59,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{The information's already out there.}Thông tin về nơi này đã có sẵn từ trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.50,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{In a way that looks incredibly \Nnatural, no less.}Theo một cách cực kì tự nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.20,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{See? Simple enough, right?}Hiểu chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.10,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{And she anticipated all of this\Nstarting when we fled?}Và cô ta đã tính toán hết mọi chuyện từ khi chạy trốn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.19,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{That means she knew Zoble would fall,}Tức là Miku biết Zoble sẽ bị tiêu diệt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.72,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{that we'd be cut off from communications...}và không thể liên lạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.10,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{She knew she'd use\N that internet cafe to plan out}Biết cả sử dụng cafe internet sẽ bị lộ,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.19,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{our lives as shut-ins...}cuộc sống trốn tránh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:15.54,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{She'd thought this through all the way\N to getting back in touch with the Demon Lord?}Thậm chí còn nghĩ đến cách liên lạc với quỷ vương?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:19.57,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Miku! I can't believe you \Nran off on your own!}Miku! Không thể tin cô lại bỏ chạy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.17,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Hi! That was faster than I expected.}Xin chào! Nhanh hơn tôi nghĩ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.98,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Good to see you again, Your Lordship!}Đã lâu không gặp, quỷ vương!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.39,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Stow the pleasantries, you fool!}Cái gì mà lâu chứ, con ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:31.12,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{She's so many steps ahead,\N it's honestly creepy...}Cô ta tính trước quá nhiều bước, kinh dị quá..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.15,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{You must have run a search \Nwith the perfect timing, sir.}Ngài đã tìm kiếm đúng lúc nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:39.14,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Oh, Merku? There was actually \Na set time to do that, you see.}Merku à? Thực ra đã có khoảng thời gian\Nnhất định để tìm kiếm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:43.22,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{The idea was to start searching the \Nsecond there was any major demon activity.}Đó là khi một con ác quỷ bắt đầu hoạt động, ta sẽ tìm kiếm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.89,Italics,Merku,0,0,0,,{So that was part of the plan, too, huh?}Ra đó cũng là nằm trong kế hoạch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.10,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Things were already afoot, however.}Không lâu trước...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.14,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Buzz and Meliano have been taken out.}Buzz và Meliano đã bị xử rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.57,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Huh. So that's their kid, is it?}Vậy ra là con của chúng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:59.03,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{They were probably begging for help \Nwith the baby and got killed in the process.}Chúng cầu xin kẻ địch cứu con mình và bị xử chứ gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:03.16,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Now then, Your Lordship, please tell me \Neverything you know about what's going on.}Giờ thì hãy nói tôi nghe toàn bộ mọi chuyện, Quỷ vương.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.78,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.97,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{What's with that face, Miku?}Cái mặt gì thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.86,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{I was just thinking about how boned we are.}Tôi chỉ đang nghĩ ngợi nhiều chuyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.59,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{With Piscalat's crew being brainwashed,}Nhóm Piscalat đã bị tẩy não,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:19.92,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{all we've got left is Kuraishi, \NFerlandia, Kroft, and Raki!}chúng ta chỉ còn Kuraishi, Ferlandia, Kroft và Raki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.86,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{We are thoroughly screwed! \NCan we just give up?}Chịu thôi! Bỏ cuộc nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.43,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{That's extra disheartening \Ncoming from you, so knock it off!}Đừng có suy nghĩ tiêu cực và chán nản nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:27.81,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Right now, I need research facilities.}Lúc này ta cần nghiên cứu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.86,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I can't do a thing in a hovel like this!}Ta không thể làm gì với bộ dạng này được!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:34.68,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{I think Kuraishi has got you covered there, \Nso why not rendezvous with him?}Tôi nghĩ Kuraishi cũng đã\N giúp ngài, sao không tái hợp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.69,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{And how would I do that?}Và bằng cách nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.17,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{Can't you do it the same way you found Miku?}Ngài không làm được như Miku sao?
