Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.80,Main,Teta,0,0,0,,{Miku-neechan, I'm back. I brought food.}Em về rồi nè chị Miku. Mua đồ ăn rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.46,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, Teta-kun!}Về rồi hả Teta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.48,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{What now? Do you want to eat?}Sao? Em muốn ăn trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.35,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Or would you rather play first?}Hay phịch chị trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.81,Main,Teta,0,0,0,,{U-Um... I wanna play first.}E-Em muốn phịch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.18,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{You're such a needy boy, aren't you?}Đúng là trai hư mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:19.82,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Do you want to play with me\N or Merku-oneechan today?}Em muốn phịch chị nào? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.82,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{This lifestyle is so debauched...}Cái cuộc sống sai trái này...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.07,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{A little }{\i1}{too}{\i0}{ debauched!}Thật đáng xấu hổ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.16,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Nah.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.83,Main,Merku,0,0,0,,{I'm honestly disgusted with \Nhow much I'm enjoying it.}Và tôi thật kinh tởm khi cảm thấy sướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.64,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{H-Hey, isn't she that fugitive?}N-Này, con nhỏ trong lệnh truy nã kìa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:36.41,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{The one worth 100 mill?!}100 triệu đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.71,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{Hurry and take a shot!}Nhanh chụp ảnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.71,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Make sure you get my good side, okay?}Chụp cho đẹp vào nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.25,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Hello?! Hello?!}Xin chào? Xin chào?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.39,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{Yes, it's the that fugitive on the poster!}Là kẻ bị truy nã!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:44.47,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Right, she's on walking \Ndown the street in Central!}Cô ta đang đi dạo ở đường trung tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.47,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,Vậy là phải chia tiền thưởng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.36,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,{Miku's on Central Road!}Miku đang ở đại lộ trung tâm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.07,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,{Reports are flooding in!}Thông tin đang tràn ngập!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.54,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,{I want that video here! Now!}Mau đưa video đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.98,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,{Come on, you can get a closer shot than that!}Thôi nào, quay gần hơn đi cho rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:53.92,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Is this really her?}Là cô ta à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.68,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Yes. That voice and appearance\N are definitely Miku's.}Vâng, giọng này chắc chắn là Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.23,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{But what is she after?}Nhưng cô ta muốn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:06.11,Main,Muscles,0,0,0,,{Screw this! If I just catch her myself, \Nthat means I get the whole reward!}Phiền quá! Để tao bắt nó rồi lãnh thưởng nào!
